1. *Nekog* od njih će morati da zamene. (Someone of them will have to be replaced.)
2. Oni su tražili *nekog* da im pomogne. (They were looking for someone to help them.)
3. Ona je tražila *nekog* da je prati. (She was looking for someone to accompany her.)
4. Oni su tražili *nekog* da im pomogne da pronađu put. (They were looking for someone to help them find the way.)
5. On je tražio *nekog* da mu pomogne da završi posao. (He was looking for someone to help him finish the job.)
6. Oni su tražili *nekog* da im pomogne da istraže. (They were looking for someone to help them investigate.)